      </div>

      <div class="triptych">
        <div class="mat" data-reveal>
          <span class="ghost-num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
          <div class="mat-inner">
            <p class="eyebrow mat-eyebrow">Plant-based acetate</p>
            <h3>Made from cotton and wood pulp, not oil.</h3>
            <p>It cuts warmer, polishes glassier, and returns to the earth at the end of its long life.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mat" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="120">
          <span class="ghost-num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
          <div class="mat-inner">
            <p class="eyebrow mat-eyebrow">Carl Zeiss lenses</p>
            <h3>German glass, ground for the north.</h3>
            <p>Every pair leaves with 100% UV400, polarized Zeiss glass — cut to tame the low, hard glare you only get this far north.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mat" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="240">
          <span class="ghost-num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
          <div class="mat-inner">
            <p class="eyebrow mat-eyebrow">Hand-finished in Reykjavík</p>
            <h3>Tumbled three days, assembled by hand.</h3>
            <p>Inspected one frame at a time by the small team that designed it. Built to be kept, not replaced.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══════════ CONSCIENCE — 04 stat strip ══════════ -->
  <section class="section" aria-label="Conscience">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-head" data-reveal>
        <p class="eyebrow">04 — Conscience</p>
        <h2 class="d-l" style="margin-top:16px;">The most sustainable frame is the one you never need to <em>replace.</em></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-strip" data-reveal-group>
        <div class="stat">
          <p class="stat-num">2<span class="u">-yr</span></p>
          <p>Guarantee on every frame &amp; lens, repairs included.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <p class="stat-num">100<span class="u">%</span></p>
          <p>Plant-based bio-acetate across the collection.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <p class="stat-num">0</p>
          <p>Single-use plastic in our packaging — paper and cork only.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <p class="stat-num">1<span class="u">%</span></p>
          <p>Of revenue to Icelandic glacier conservation.</p>
